        "description": "The Ocean Course is a golf course located on Kiawah Island, South Carolina. It is known for its stunning ocean views and challenging layout. The course was designed by Pete Dye and opened in 1991. It has hosted several major golf tournaments, including the Ryder Cup and the PGA Championship; regularly ranked as one of the top 5 courses in the world.",
