        "name": "Caledonia Golf and Fish Club",
        "designer": "Mike Strantz",
        "description": "Caledonia Golf and Fish Club is a golf course located in Pawleys Island, South Carolina. The course was designed by Mike Strantz and opened in 1998. It has received numerous accolades for its beauty and playability, making it a popular destination for golfers.",
        "personal_anecdote": "If Kiawah is on the ocean; Caledonia is in the swamp. Cut out of the marshes of the Waccamaw River, it is a unique and beautiful course. You will fail to find someone that cuts a dogfight out of the natural terrain as well as the late Mike Strantz. Caledonia and it's sister course True Blue are a must play for the enthusiast.",
